.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
House: tower, townhouse, wooden, gothic-revival, futuristic
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, pop, blues, jazz, funk
The people have 5 different jobs:  teacher, designer, analyst, software-developer, fisherman
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, comedy, sports, fantasy, musical
1. the tower house is the person who likes red
2. the swedish house is the person watching sports movies
3. the townhouse house is the fan of jazz
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the fan of pop
6. the analyst is the person watching comedy movies
7. the person who likes yellow is the designer
8. the fan of blues is in the middle
9. the gothic-revival house is on the far left
10. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies
11. the person watching musicals movies is on the left or right of the designer
12. the teacher is the fan of d&b
13. the wooden house is the software-developer
14. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the fisherman is on the left or right of the fan of funk

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| House	|   gothic-revival	|    townhouse	|    tower	|    wooden	|    swedish	|
| Movie-Genre		|     horror	|    musical	|     comedy	|     fantasy	|      sports	|
| Music-Genre	|    funk	|     jazz	|     blues	|    pop	|      d&b	|
| Job		|   designer	|    fisherman	|  analyst	|    software-developer	|   teacher	|
